Package: org.ajoberstar.grgit.operation

[Groovy] Class RemoteAddOp

    • org.ajoberstar.grgit.operation.RemoteAddOp
    • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
      java.util.concurrent.Callable

      class RemoteAddOp
extends java.lang.Object

      Adds a remote to the repository. Returns the newly created Remote. If remote with given name already exists, its URIs are replaced with newly specified ones.

      To add remote.

       grgit.remote.add(name: 'new-remote', url: 'git@github.com:username/project.git')
      See git-remote Manual Page.
      See Also:
      git-remote Manual Page
